{"tid":1509312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"場運動經歷左咁多日 好心你地分析下d資訊先啦","createTime":"2019-08-26T19:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T04:53:58.000Z","uid":2988,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83f46be776e99cc1a5c213a9acd46e4fab986073","tid":1509312,"uid":2988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:53:51.000Z","msg":"連登不嬲有好多人開post<br />\n試圖去分化大家 嚇大家 <br />\n等大家唔好出去<br />\n求奇打幾隻字 再加句fc左 <br />\n之後又會有大把人信哂係真消息咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好心你地自己睇完都分析下啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1505972/page/10\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1505972/page/10</a><br />\n琴日 27歲比人打到入icu個單野<br />\n樓主開頭話fc左 問左<span style=\"color: red;\">當時人老豆老母</span><br />\n成個post連張圖都無 <br />\n結果到最後發現 原來佢個fc 係問<span style=\"color: red;\">自己老母</span><br />\n係佢老母嚇鳩佢唔想佢出去先講大話 然後一眾連登仔比樓主撚哂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508928\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508928</a><br />\n跟住呢個post <br />\n就咁話一個朋友做黑警 然後有個對話圖<br />\n就話有人比人強姦左 個兇手叫XX榮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母 黑警朋友同你講就當fc左 連證明佢朋友就係黑警都無</span></span><br />\n好明顯係想令到女手足唔敢再行出黎抗爭<br />\n同之前個單接放學比人強姦一樣 <br />\n乜証據都無就亂傳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507788\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507788</a><br />\n仲有好多好多都係未經證實就貼上黎連登<br />\n<br />\n連登每日都有幾千甚至有萬幾個post<br />\n希望大家真係可以分析下先好再傳出去<br />\n如果唔係大家只會害到好多手足"},{"pid":"2d2f232169c0a120421d3c5b4f06ca2bf2e49e4c","tid":1509312,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrjbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=d60ed23c\" data-auto-